    "Name": "Maxim APC",
    "Details": "An odd experimental design, the Maxim Flanker is designed to increase the hovercraft's performance while dropping troops, it has much more armor on its right side than on its left side. The idea was to present a heavily-armored broadside to the enemy while performing its primary duty. \n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Biome Restrictions: This unit can not deploy in Lunar or Martian biomes due to using an ICE.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 8/12 hexes / 240/360 meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Ferro-Fibrous\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>        95     25\n<b>Left</b>          50     25\n<b>Right</b>       220     25\n<b>Rear</b>         60     25\n<b>Turret</b>       95     25\n\n<b>Total</b>      520    125</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Rugged</color>",
    "Icon": "Maxim"
  },
